reviews.review_text: Very Nice Sounds great!  I was at this show, loved being in Florida for a few days in early April, coming from CT.  The show was solid and well played.  Listening to this recording brought back memories of inside the venue and out in the lawn parking area. Thanks again Charlie Miller!
